      "comment": "DOONGALLA PARODY (8) has a strong record this trip with two wins and three placings from six starts. In the money last time at this track (26.11) in a Mix 6/7, finishing a 2.25 lengths second. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. NO EXIT (6) had second look this course and distance latest and improved on his time, finishing a 2.5 lengths second in 26.17. Will be in this for a long way. DARING BANDIT (7) finished fifth last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 350m at Healesville, taking a Bottom Up - Grade 7 in an excellent 19.20. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. VELVET LASS (1) cannot be underestimated.",
